doc.after: A user with CheckUser access will get an extra "CheckUser" option under Special:SpecialPages, a "Check IP addresses" option on Special:Contributions, access to Special:CheckUser and Special:CheckUserLog special pages, and other similar functions. On the English Wikipedia, CheckUsers also receive access to the Checkuser-l global mailing list, subscription to functionaries-l, and access to the IRC channels if they so request.
